{{see|Dawn}}
==English==
===Etymology===
A back-formation from [[dawning]].

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|dawn||}}

# {{intransitive}} To [[begin]] to brighten with daylight.
#: ''Before a new day '''dawns'''.''
# {{intransitive}} To start to appear or be [[realize]]d.
#: ''I don't want to be there when the truth '''dawns''' on him.''

