===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# The [[rising]] of the [[sun]].
# {{uncountable}} The [[time]] when the sun rises.
#: ''She rose before '''dawn''' to meet the train.''
# {{uncountable}} The [[beginning]].
#: ''The '''dawn''' of civilisation.''

